name: multiversedot0019
description: That the wealthy do not hold back when it comes to extravagant parties is known across the entire multiverse. On Gralgazaah, a planet just a few clicks away from Earth, the great Grilmau (gender unknown) is known to spare no expense and ignore any morality. Pictured here is an alien they used as a decorative pillar at their parties. Everyone who is anyone in the multiverse is invited to these. So far nobody from Earth has attended.
